# Cloudflare Pages redirects
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# Evaluation order: first match wins. Static rules first, wildcards later.

# Clean-URL canonicalisation: .html extensions 301 to extensionless paths.
# Activates on Cloudflare Pages. GitHub Pages does not honour this file.
/index.html    /         301
/about.html    /about    301
/course.html   /course   301
/contact.html  /contact  301
/apply.html    /apply    301

# www apex canonicalisation is handled at the Cloudflare zone level
# (DNS + Redirect Rule), not here. Documented in
# docs/infra/cloudflare-setup-runbook.md Part 3.
